= Referrals

== Send Referrals

Request a referral code email that contains a deep link to mobile app:

[source]
[cols="2,1,5"]
|===
|Name |Type |Description

|`user` | `integer` | ID of user making referral.
|`email` | `string` | The request email address.
|`type` | `string` | Type of request. Set to `invite-referral`.

|===

[source]
----
POST /referrals
----

=== Input

[cols="2,1,5"]
|===
|Name |Type |Description

|`email` | `string` | The email to send the referral code too.
|===


